description._content: Description: Troodos. View towards Troodos, Spring (from near mile-stone 26) Location: Troodos, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Description: Troodos. Natural regeneration of Aleppo Pine Troodos Forest; 3000 ft. elevation. Trees 10 years old from seed sown. Location: Troodos, Cyprus Date: 1920-1930 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/697 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
